________________________________________
20. Best Practice
Preferred exposure order:
1️⃣ Route / Ingress
2️⃣ LoadBalancer
3️⃣ NodePort
Reason:
Routes provide:
•	TLS
•	security
•	hostname routing
________________________________________
21. Chapter Concept Summary
Feature	Purpose
Route	expose HTTP/HTTPS
Ingress	HTTP routing
LoadBalancer	expose non-HTTP protocols
NodePort	expose service via node port
MetalLB	load balancer for bare metal
IPAddressPool	range of external IPs
L2Advertisement	ARP announcements
________________________________________
22. Important DO280 Exam Concepts
You should remember:
•	Routes only support HTTP/HTTPS
•	LoadBalancer exposes TCP services
•	MetalLB provides load balancing for bare metal clusters
•	IPAddressPool defines IP range
•	Layer2 uses ARP
•	Layer3 uses BGP

